{"tid":2131323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"投訴無醫生　武漢女護士墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-07-29T19:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:09:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":331,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"16fcc9ff065086189e881f02ff94f83b966e66c7","tid":2131323,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200730/S4KDAHH324RLCO6WNWVPBSYWQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200730%2FS4KDAHH324RLCO6WNWVPBSYWQU%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=62b2da05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200730%2FS4KDAHH324RLCO6WNWVPBSYWQU%2F&h=3652239e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200730/S4KDAHH324RLCO6WNWVPBSYWQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n湖北武漢協和醫院（圖）昨有隔離病房女護士墮樓身亡。據悉，死者生前多番投訴醫生尸位素餐，從不巡房，甚至要求懷孕八個月的護士去巡房，同事們都十分支持她。家屬向本報表示，武漢肺炎爆發以來，死者壓力已很多，也曾聽聞有護士實名投訴，「但沒想到是她」。"},{"pid":"2635e9ae7a31138742b5f5d7691821acaf371318","tid":2131323,"uid":25601,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2tYfkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2tYfkd.jpg&h=862f7fa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af23d12587ec965a69060b779c5a59a4e327e2e3","tid":2131323,"uid":25601,"like":127,"dislike":4,"score":123,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTh2G0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTh2G0p.jpg&h=d5c26966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0c96r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0c96r5.jpg&h=450a9d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YERyOFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYERyOFr.jpg&h=0522ba15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":